Objective:

Develop a debugging tool for inter-process communication (IPC) methods
(pipes, message queues, shared memory) with a GUI that simulates data transfer,
highlights bottlenecks, and detects deadlocks.

Technology Stack:
Backend: C++ (for IPC mechanisms, data handling, and debugging logic)

Frontend: HTML, Tailwind CSS (for the GUI)

IPC Methods Covered: Pipes, Message Queues, Shared Memory
